Additionally, the paper mentions the use of geometric priors, which could suggest that it belongs to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The use of wavelet filters could also suggest that it belongs to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the mention of object image databases could suggest that it belongs to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
